\$8{,}000 \cdot 4.623 = \$36{,}984
\dfrac{1}{(1.08)^{1}} + \dfrac{1}{(1.08)^{2}} + ... +\dfrac{1}{(1.08)^{6}}=4.623
\dfrac{8000}{(1.08)^{1}} + \dfrac{8000}{(1.08)^{2}} + ... +\dfrac{8000}{(1.08)^{6}}=36984
\left(\dfrac{1}{(1.08)^{1}} + \dfrac{1}{(1.08)^{2}} + ... +\dfrac{1}{(1.08)^{6}}\right)\times8000=4.623\times8000
